Game ......: Sega Bass Fishing
Date ...: 2003.11.13
Video ..: PAL
Rip notes .: nothing ripped

Rod. Reel. Lure. Weather. Time. Temperature. Location. It all matters if you want to land the biggest fish in the lake. Use all your experience and trickery to see if you can bait the bass. Morning? Go surface lure. Hot? Better drop down to cooler water. 
 
- All new DC exclusive game modes 
- Amazing AI ; fish react realistically to changing conditions and lure types 
- 8 unique fishing locations rendered in gorgeous 3d graphics 
- 14 different lures, each with unique performance
- Real-time underwater camera anles
- Compatible with fishing controller for the most lifelike experience possible 